{"tid":1474013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"817光復紅土，還我靜土！","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:29:05.000Z","uid":218684,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"147fe61e35576368aa241df3401277ffcb0eccc4","tid":1474013,"uid":218684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tYcDiqy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYcDiqy.jpg&h=680a131d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見無咩人講817，其實紅土都需要香港人關注！<br />\n自從機場搬走咗之後，九龍城區嘅居民有一段時間過住平靜嘅生活，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不過！</span></span><br />\n內地旅行團大規模踴入紅磡及土瓜灣，造成交通阻塞同混亂！<br />\n另外舊區多「百五個」已經成為常態！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家仲記得4月喺土瓜灣，有架旅遊巴撞死咗一個女人，短暫地引起社會嘅關注...然後就無然後了。<br />\n<br />\n所以，喺816同818之間，呢個寂寂無名嘅地區，都希望大家可以幫下手！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">817，光復紅土，還我靜土！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fd9ac28ce918ddba5e574fe87485487396f28b08","tid":1474013,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70bbf11fdc91a404435cbab51babf631df3295bf","tid":1474013,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"紅土人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03f25283965b6ab5f7e0f02b67d29ff8e3b08ec","tid":1474013,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff1fcd09a717f27cc533caab51c760ca2a730e3","tid":1474013,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56e8dc216095fc1a8deb33b9eca8a80caafa67f3","tid":1474013,"uid":218684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"紅土攻略小參考:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414663</a>"},{"pid":"08053eb88e8ce32b813536d8140b2d85091e4d19","tid":1474013,"uid":207505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"黃埔11號晚發生嘅事好多人都唔知<br />\n得啲街坊行緊街 無啦啦3架狗車嚟咗<br />\n啲防暴警係度逗啲無辜街坊<br />\n仲要話人集會<br />\n明明全部都係途人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1LcpDmFVcm/?igshid=y2wa2dnvrfbv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1LcpDmFVcm%2F%3Figshid%3Dy2wa2dnvrfbv&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=d4de1b4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1LcpDmFVcm%2F%3Figshid%3Dy2wa2dnvrfbv&h=5841e75d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1LcpDmFVcm/?igshid=y2wa2dnvrfbv</a><br />\n搞啲大批街坊走落嚟屌走佢哋<br />\n點知黃埔花園第二邊又有狗車<br />\n仲舉藍旗話街坊非法集會<br />\n街坊冒住雨都繼續屌狗<br />\n黃埔街坊繼撚保安十個鐘又一傑作<br />\n你哋唔係唔撐下話？"},{"pid":"d4bd7dc4add6a98acf5e9b264065c0796ce7fb23","tid":1474013,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass